# 🎓 Marksheet Management System (MySQL Project)

This is a simple **Marksheet Management System** project using **MySQL**.

It stores students' subject-wise marks, calculates **Total**, **Percentage**, and **Grade** — everything in a clean and easy format.

---

## 📦 Features

- Store subject-wise marks
- Calculate total & percentage
- Grade system (A+, A, B, C, Fail)
- 100 Marks per subject
- Easy to modify and scale

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- MySQL (Structured Query Language)
- GitHub for project management

---

## 🧱 Database Structure

### 🔹 Database Name

```sql
CREATE DATABASE simple_marksheet;
USE simple_marksheet;
